dialogue: I did a trade-mark search on all of the excellent product names you suggested.
Every one of them is taken.
So I did a search on the names that weren't so great.
Then I checked on the names Icrud, ipuke, eatdirt-anddie, and defectiveproduct.
So our new product name will be a combination of grunts and shrieks.
Ours sounds more like a monkey passing a kidney stone.
